SGHA 3 port air operated high pressure coolant valve, for high pressure coolant liquid (up to 3.0 MPa/7.0 MPa). Ideal for lubrication, dust blowing and cooling. Cv of 1.8 to 6.5. Pilot air pressure used is 0.25 to 0.7 MPa.
